short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension checks your expenses on OpenAI.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The "OpenAI Expenses Checker" Chrome extension is a faster and simpler alternative to using a website. With the extension, you can access expense tracking directly from your browser, saving time and eliminating the need to navigate a separate site. It offers a streamlined interface, integrates seamlessly with the browser, and provides real-time updates and notifications, making expense management quick and easy.
